goals__remit:
Coceral objectives are to represent and promote the interests of the grain, feedstuffs, rice, olive oil and agro-supply trade associations operating within Europe; 
to proactively monitor and guide EU policy makers in market, food safety and environmental matters; 
to promote strategies for provision of safe food ingredients and feed raw materials for the benfit of EU processors and consumers; 
to publish reports and position papers for stakeholders.
